gs hotkeyed, 2 non hotkeyed (mana song is the 8th slot, I use ctrl-8 to activate it too, since it's not all that important to get up in that split second). I keep my mouse free for other things, like switching instruments while switching target in mid cast and moving around (very useful during CC, bards can switch target while casting a song on another target). <p><font face="poor richard" color="0000FF"><b>Ryolas Songdivine</b></font><BR>53 lvl Master of the Jig<BR><i>Remember kids, sow is only one letter away from slow!</i><BR><BR><font face="olde english" color="FF6600"<b>Kinoel Feuerfaust</b></font><BR>55 lvl Glass Cannon<BR><i>Welcome to my Barbecue!</i><BR><BR><b>Quintessence of Honour</b><BR>Lanys T'Vyl</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.showMessageRange?topicID=417.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.showPrevMessage?topicID=417.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.showNextMessage?topicID=417.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=417.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/bluesparty/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.emailToFriend?topicID=417.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.threadControl?topicID=417.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumbard.subscribeUnregisteredToT